{"tid":2368653,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[ NBA 戰線 ] 德洲民主左派Super Star KOL危機管理，真係好驚德獨","createTime":"2021-01-16T11:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T23:32:42.000Z","uid":70487,"like":10,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c84bee98f5ea6b2b413348c54d9c00522c56c914","tid":2368653,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T11:21:46.000Z","msg":"前德洲火箭隊Adidas最大粒星James Harden，<br />\n近日突然誇張轉去Brooklyn Nets組成超級球星陣容<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩具撚又贏，NBA2K遊戲都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\">但係睇真啲 原來Brooklyn Nets背景唔惹少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BqCVPsX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBqCVPsX.png&h=ce99c9d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"><a href=\"https://www.nba.com/nets/news/2020/01/15/brooklyn-nets-to-celebrate-life-and-legacy-of-dr-martin-luther-king-jr-this-monday-jan-18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nba.com%2Fnets%2Fnews%2F2020%2F01%2F15%2Fbrooklyn-nets-to-celebrate-life-and-legacy-of-dr-martin-luther-king-jr-this-monday-jan-18&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyJhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=37bd3f99\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nba.com/nets/news/2020/01/15/brooklyn-nets-to-celebrate-life-and-legacy-of-dr-martin-luther-king-jr-this-monday-jan-18</a></span><br />\nnBLMa<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></p> <br />\n咁大手筆 明眼人一睇就知，<br />\n點解要呢個時期換走德洲當家球星<br />\n最合理推測就係左派憂慮Texas前景。(FBI收到風<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n加上新隊超級球星陣容:<br />\n2個Nike簽名系列球星(沾屎同級)<br />\n1個Adidas<br />\n兩間體育用品同支共咩關係就唔洗多講<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/5Wl2cg6roGc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5Wl2cg6roGc&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyJhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=f527a935\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5Wl2cg6roGc</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論 : <br />\n1月20日之後美國會發生咩事大家拭目以待，<br />\n總統一直都是由人民決定的。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"right\"><span class=\"medium\"><ins>延伸閱讀</ins></span><br />\n<span class=\"small\">[ NBA 戰線 ]  皇帝占香港人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2125686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2125686</a><br />\n！！！ 解通民主左派=支共 ！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2200032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2200032</a></span></p>"},{"pid":"cfba1afee70d6136be6e70d25e30a4c50126ea8b","tid":2368653,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T11:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e6491c5e03a65061194e664d0dfb514f9c2a29","tid":2368653,"uid":70487,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T11:28:56.000Z","msg":"登伯 : 堅決反對任何分裂國土行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f19c80f584ceb043cbba27bb469e1c67da8610","tid":2368653,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T11:36:41.000Z","msg":"留得Joe哥在，哪怕無德洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbd0022c65386c0455b599a80fb489a7774d39f","tid":2368653,"uid":70487,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"如果覺得球員轉會無政治原因，<br />\n咁你根本就唔識bALL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個球星代表一整個城市，<br />\n尤其身負咁多廣告宣傳價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n左派最愛打造KOL吸睛"},{"pid":"f1bd0dd5694316da4578339ad196aeb03910044d","tid":2368